{"tid":140072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"望住宜家班中學生真係心酸","createTime":"2017-03-02T02:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T04:35:16.000Z","uid":87892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86a1e79296ac4fdfa471968a2ca9459ca21ae257","tid":140072,"uid":87892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"早前幫學生做生捱輔導規劃，睇到幾種學生<br />\n每次都覺得好百感交雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.明明考到5**既Level分數但同你講我唔想讀U再受罪，出來做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （呢個我覺得好灰）<br />\n2.連入職表都唔識得填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 面試見西廚，問識得整咩，搭你中菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見設計師，我期望個學生答我IA，Photoshop，佢答我識得斟茶遞水比老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你叫條友自我介紹答你我唔識，自己睇資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.成績唔係靚，但起碼發奮同你講努力讀上去，無U唔緊要，唔怕HD Asso，最緊要讀到自己心儀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.成績平平凡凡，部分仲要爛Grade到仆街，同你講大學除左頭三間唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後同你講U垃圾來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5.高分，但唔知自己做緊乜，個前途好似唔關自己事，答你是但啦，無所謂，問做野又答你唔知，讀唔讀又話屋企人話事，反正自己無人權，寵物來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講，我覺得自己中六果陣已經無左以前既中七學生AL果班風範，但宜家出來做野半工讀見到班學生真心覺得慘<br />\n宜家個社會做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211c8de722adb3cc8fbd55bce57bc256a1058558","tid":140072,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"似假膠hea 鳩你wo<br />\n中學雞不嬲唔鍾意呢d 乜乜計劃既活動"},{"pid":"5510319c3839d8100c85cbf8d5568afefb6e94a8","tid":140072,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:01:11.000Z","msg":"樓主你有乜撚資格幫人規劃？"},{"pid":"fac34762f435994739d256329b250e69bda6a7f2","tid":140072,"uid":34336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}